Sauce Runner for Virtual devices
---------------------------------

Sauce runner for virtual devices is used to run Espresso tests on sauce emulators. Here is an example to test on two devices.

./sauce-runner-virtual \
  -u test_user \
  -k 1234-1235 \
  -f espresso \
  -a ./helloworld.apk \
  -t ./helloworld-AndroidTest.apk \
  -d 'deviceName=Samsung Galaxy S8 HD GoogleAPI Emulator,platformVersion=7.0' \
  -d 'deviceName=Google Pixel GoogleAPI Emulator,platformVersion=7.1'  

Please refer to the following link for documentation:
https://wiki.saucelabs.com/display/DOCS/Command+Reference+for+Sauce+Runner+for+Virtual+Devices 
